import React, { Component } from 'react';
import Button from 'react-bootstrap/Button';
import ButtonToolbar from 'react-bootstrap/Button';
import 'App.css';
class Letters extends Component {
    render(){
        return (
           [<ButtonToolbar>
          <Button variant="primary">A</Button>
          <Button variant="primary">B</Button>
          <Button variant="primary">C</Button>
          <Button variant="primary">D</Button>
          <Button variant="primary">E</Button>
          <Button variant="primary">F</Button>
          <Button variant="primary">G</Button>
          <Button variant="primary">H</Button>          
          <Button variant="primary">I</Button> 
          <Button variant="primary">J</Button> 
          <Button variant="primary">K</Button>   
          <Button variant="primary">L</Button> 
          <Button variant="primary">M</Button>      
          </ButtonToolbar>,
           <ButtonToolbar>
           <Button variant="primary">N</Button>
           <Button variant="primary">O</Button>
           <Button variant="primary">P</Button>
           <Button variant="primary">Q</Button>
           <Button variant="primary">R</Button>
           <Button variant="primary">S</Button>
           <Button variant="primary">T</Button>          
           <Button variant="primary">U</Button> 
           <Button variant="primary">V</Button> 
           <Button variant="primary">W</Button>   
           <Button variant="primary">X</Button>   
           <Button variant="primary">Y</Button>  
           <Button variant="primary">Z</Button>  
           </ButtonToolbar>]
        );
    }
}
export default Letters;
